step.screen:
ACCREDITATION RANGE:
classification= UNCLASSIFIED; all compartment combinations valid;
* i is new in this file classification= INTERNAL_USE_ONLY; all compartment combinations valid;
* n is new in this file classification= NEED_TO_KNOW; all compartment combinations valid;
classification= CONFIDENTIAL; all compartment combinations valid except: c c a c b
classification= SECRET; only valid compartment combinations: . . . * r is new in this file classification= REGISTERED; all compartment combinations valid;

minimum clearance= u; 
minimum sensitivity label= u; 
minimum protect as classification= u;

